				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/B%E1%BB%87nh-b%C3%A1ch/poem-R10HTH0Yj1d7m74FFFpbMw">Bệnh bách - 病柏</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Phi-Khanh/H%E1%BA%A1-kinh-tri%E1%BB%87u-do%C3%A3n-Nguy%E1%BB%85n-C%C3%B4ng-vi-V%C3%A2n-%C4%90%E1%BB%93n-kinh-l%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3c-s%E1%BB%A9/poem-GpNNsgruTdR4BLzfUXNi5Q">Hạ kinh triệu doãn Nguyễn Công vi Vân Đồn kinh lược sứ - 賀京兆尹阮公為雲屯經略使</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Phi-Khanh/author-3K5mDhkNpasGeB0z-64AmA">Nguyễn Phi Khanh</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-Trinh/Khu%C3%AA-t%E1%BB%AB-k%E1%BB%B3-4/poem-xCNJtofKS7G-gvWpc_XOBA">Khuê từ kỳ 4 - 閨詞其四</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-Trinh/author-HrCILDC9soRz0JVGAcDF9w">Lê Trinh</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/K%C3%BD-t%C3%B2ng-t%C3%B4n-S%C3%B9ng-Gi%E1%BA%A3n/poem-ngKf_5JoJSSbVa3yOZ-MdA">Ký tòng tôn Sùng Giản - 寄從孫崇簡</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Chu-Di-T%C3%B4n/Ng%E1%BB%8Dc-%C4%91%E1%BB%9Bi-sinh-ca/poem-XGDV-KqgVFWcId2MqnewVg">Ngọc đới sinh ca - 玉帶生歌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Chu-Di-T%C3%B4n/author-edTceA8S1YU0BsK54Tjq9Q">Chu Di Tôn</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADm/Ph%E1%BB%A5ng-ch%E1%BB%89-tr%C3%B9ng-khai-Thi%C3%AAn-Uy-c%E1%BA%A3ng-cung-k%C3%BD/poem-BXH7PoB6L8J7QsWWlH77rQ">Phụng chỉ trùng khai Thiên Uy cảng cung ký - 奉旨重開天威港恭記</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADm/author-14GcnhLjD2ajP0MTgtX13Q">Ngô Thì Nhậm</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BA%B7ng-Minh-Khi%C3%AAm/S%C4%A9-V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/poem-TG4k72IxpLtK1JXgb6lylg">Sĩ Vương - 士王</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BA%B7ng-Minh-Khi%C3%AAm/author-P_O0C8eAMSSE0VWCvRAM-w">Đặng Minh Khiêm</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C3%82u-D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Huy%E1%BB%81n/T%E1%BA%B7ng-ho%E1%BA%A1-c%C3%B4ng-L%C3%AA-Tr%E1%BB%8Dng-C%E1%BA%A9n/poem-lvIylIRVDQBW7fQ3YQkRQg">Tặng hoạ công Lê Trọng Cẩn - 贈畫工黎仲瑾</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C3%82u-D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Huy%E1%BB%81n/author-c9sc_sRxr6NeSR_7fPmfbg">Âu Dương Huyền</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%E1%BA%A9m-D%C3%A3/Th%C3%A1i-li%C3%AAn-kh%C3%BAc/poem-R1aFMboRI7ZeS45BSpmhTQ">Thái liên khúc - 採蓮曲</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%E1%BA%A9m-D%C3%A3/author-y6iidl9JMeYlXAHrQDdILQ">Thẩm Dã</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/V%C4%83n-H%E1%BB%99c-T%C6%B0-l%E1%BB%A5c-quan-v%E1%BB%8B-quy/poem-LB7dbbdCGM-hnrqEfAiwyw">Văn Hộc Tư lục quan vị quy - 聞斛斯六官未歸</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br></div>	</div>
